00w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_englishteacher_billieeilish_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_englishteacher_billieeilish_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_englishteacher_billieeilish_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_englishteacher_billieeilish_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2024_englishteacher_billieeilish_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">英语老师</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>最近的单曲《Birds Of A Feather》的舒缓封面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-english-teacher-interview-richard-hawley-3770672">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：英语老师讲述理查德·霍利音乐的“经典、永恒”力量</a></strong></li></ul><p>周二（7 月 16 日），这些冉冉升起的独立摇滚歌手和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-english-teacher-the-worlds-biggest-paving-slab-3495785"><em>NME</em>封面明星</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/radio-1">BBC 广播 1 台</a><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m0020vf6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>杰克·桑德斯的新音乐秀</em></a>上表演了这首歌曲的悲观版本。你可以在下面听一下。</p><p>在谈到她为什么要翻唱这张专辑时，主唱莉莉·方丹 (Lily Fontaine) 说道：“我记得我们选择翻唱的那一刻，我听着这首歌，我哭了，然后我把它发给了小伙子们。我想，‘好吧，这首歌很受欢迎，而且很好听’，就是这样。”</p><p>这首歌由 Eilish 于 7 月 2 日发行，还出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/heartstopper"><em>Heartstopper</em></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-a-preview-of-new-billie-eilish-song-in-heartstopper-season-three-trailer-3756116">第三季的预告片中</a>，取自她最近的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">《Hit Me Hard And Soft》</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="英语老师 - BIRDS OF A FEATHER（Billie Eilish 封面）"