w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/DeadpoolWolverine-soundtrack-tracklist-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/DeadpoolWolverine-soundtrack-tracklist-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/DeadpoolWolverine-soundtrack-tracklist-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/DeadpoolWolverine-soundtrack-tracklist-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/DeadpoolWolverine-soundtrack-tracklist-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/marvel">漫威</a>发布了<em>《死侍与金刚狼》</em>原声带，收录了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stray-kids">Stray Kids</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼</a>等人的歌曲 - 请查看下面的完整曲目列表。</p><p>这部超级英雄电影将于下周五（7 月 26 日）在全球影院上映。继<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/deadpool-2-film-review-2314606"><em>《死侍 2》</em></a> （2018 年）之后，续集由瑞恩·雷诺兹 (Ryan Reynolds) 联合编剧，他继续饰演再生反英雄，与休·杰克曼 (Hugh Jackman) 饰演变种<em>人 X 战警</em>人物。</p><p><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/deadpool-2-film-review-2314606"><b>《死侍 2》——评论：</b></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/deadpool-2-film-review-2314606"><b>近乎完美的作品</b></a></p><p><em>《死侍》和《金刚狼》</em>将见证这两个同名角色最终融入<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙</a>，这是继 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-marvels-review-brie-larson-3532201"><em>《漫威》</em></a>之后，漫威电影宇宙“第五阶段”的最新作品。</p><p>官方配乐由 18 首曲目组成，包括 Green Day 1997 年的单曲“Good Riddance (Time Of Your Life)”、Stray Kids 即将推出的原创歌曲“Slash”以及艾薇儿 2002 年的民谣“I&#39;m With You”。</p><p>还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/n-sync">*NSYNC</a> （“Bye Bye Bye”）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fergie">Fergie</a> （“Glamorous”）的 00 年代流行歌曲，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/huey-lewis-the-news">Huey Lewis &amp; The News</a> （“The Power Of Love”）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/goo-goo-dolls">Goo Goo Dolls（“Goo Goo Dolls</a> ”）的经典吉他曲调。 &#39;鸢尾花&#39;）。</p><p>此外，明星杰克曼的 2017 年音乐剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-greatest-showman"><em>《马戏之王》</em></a>中的“The Greatest Show”也出现在曲目列表中。它出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-newton-john">奥利维亚·牛顿-约翰</a>和约翰·特拉沃尔塔的《<em>油脂》</em> （1978）中的“你是我想要的”之前的专辑中。</p><p><a href="https://www.disneymusicemporium.com/product/XVLP273" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订黑胶版</a>，并查看下面的公告。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9h5xkSJ8q4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 